Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.37,0:00:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,On behalf of the Governing Body,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.72,0:00:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,we warmly commend you for your desire
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.77,0:00:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,to expand your service to Jehovah
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.93,0:00:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and your interest\Nin submitting an application
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.52,0:00:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,to serve as a temporary volunteer
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.77,0:00:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,or as a member\Nof the Worldwide Order
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.25,0:00:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,of Special Full-Time Servants
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.17,0:00:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,of Jehovah’s Witnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.11,0:00:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,By making yourself available\Nto serve in this unique way,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.07,0:00:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,you imitate the faithful prophet Isaiah,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.08,0:00:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,who said at Isaiah 6:8:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.53,0:00:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,“Here I am! Send me!”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.38,0:00:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Submitting your application\Nmay open a door of opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.27,0:00:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,to serve Jehovah and his organization
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.82,0:00:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,in a variety of ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.09,0:00:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, there’s a place\Nfor everyone in Jehovah’s service.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.95,0:00:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether we’re working hard\Nas a congregation publisher,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.31,0:01:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,a regular pioneer, a Bethelite,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.46,0:01:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,or on a theocratic construction project,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.48,0:01:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,we have the satisfaction of knowing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.19,0:01:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that Jehovah treasures what we’re doing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.97,0:01:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,because of our heartfelt love for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.61,0:01:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hebrews 6:10 says:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.18,0:01:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,“God is not unrighteous\Nso as to forget your work
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.66,0:01:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,“and the love you showed\Nfor his name by ministering
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.67,0:01:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and continuing to minister\Nto the holy ones.”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.71,0:01:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Before submitting an application\Nfor expanded theocratic service,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.34,0:01:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,it’s important to consider prayerfully
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.10,0:01:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,how you’ll respond\Nto the questions on the application.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.18,0:01:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hebrews 13:18 says:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.25,0:01:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,“We wish to conduct ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.42,0:01:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,honestly in all things.”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.00,0:01:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So you should be honest
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.94,0:01:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,in answering the questions\Non the application,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.61,0:01:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,especially those that have to do
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.86,0:01:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,with your physical health\Nand spiritual health.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.91,0:02:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The work being done at Bethel
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.45,0:02:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and on theocratic construction projects
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.25,0:02:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,requires good physical,\Nemotional, and mental health.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.23,0:02:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,However, you may have\Na chronic health problem
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.34,0:02:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,that requires the regular attention
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.76,0:02:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,of a physician\Nor must be treated with medication.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.97,0:02:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have\Na significant limitation in this way,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.14,0:02:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,it would be better for you\Nto continue your faithful service
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.98,0:02:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,in the field\Nwith your local congregation
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.92,0:02:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and, if possible,\Nin the regular pioneer service.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.53,0:02:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If you’re not sure\Nwhether your health situation
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.78,0:02:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,would prevent you\Nfrom submitting an application,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.04,0:02:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,the elders\Nin your congregation can help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.17,0:02:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,They can review with you\Nthe specific application questions
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.21,0:02:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,that deal with health matters
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.25,0:02:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,so that you personally may determine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.76,0:02:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,whether or not you should apply.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.63,0:02:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Regardless of where we’re serving,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.55,0:03:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,we need Jehovah’s blessing\Nto be successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.02,0:03:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Psalm 127:1 says:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.96,0:03:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,“Unless Jehovah builds the house,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.73,0:03:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,“it is in vain\Nthat its builders work hard on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.24,0:03:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,“Unless Jehovah guards the city,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.20,0:03:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,it is in vain that the guard stays awake.”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.62,0:03:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But as the account\Nin Joshua chapter 7 vividly testifies,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.16,0:03:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,it’s possible for Jehovah\Nto withhold his blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.42,0:03:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember what happened
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.75,0:03:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,when Achan stole from the things
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.90,0:03:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,that were supposed\Nto be dedicated to Jehovah?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.91,0:03:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Israel lost God’s backing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.22,0:03:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Our service to Jehovah is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.14,0:03:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We cannot afford\Nto lose Jehovah’s blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.90,0:03:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,For this reason,\Nthe spiritual qualifications
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.86,0:03:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,for expanded service are high.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.15,0:04:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s expected that all of those\Noffering themselves to serve at Bethel
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.16,0:04:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,or in other theocratic assignments
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.24,0:04:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,have a clean conscience before Jehovah,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.50,0:04:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,having left behind all unclean practices
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.50,0:04:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,or immoral conduct.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.42,0:04:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,For instance,\Nthose who have viewed pornography
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.82,0:04:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,in the past year should not apply.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.88,0:04:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, if you realize
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.72,0:04:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,that you may have become involved\Nin unclean conduct
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.72,0:04:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,with someone\Nof the opposite sex or the same sex,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.02,0:04:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Jehovah very considerately explains\Nwhat we should do
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.38,0:04:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,in James 5:14, 15:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.17,0:04:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,“Is there anyone\N[spiritually] sick among you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.36,0:04:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,“Let him call the elders\Nof the congregation to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.08,0:04:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,“and let them pray over him,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.68,0:04:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,“applying oil to him\Nin the name of Jehovah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.12,0:04:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,“And the prayer of faith\Nwill make the sick one well,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.71,0:04:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,“and Jehovah will raise him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.38,0:05:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, if he has committed sins,\Nhe will be forgiven.”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.80,0:05:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,How reassuring!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.05,0:05:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have a heavy conscience\Nbecause of something you’ve done,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.50,0:05:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,you should get help to strengthen\Nyour relationship with Jehovah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.54,0:05:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You can later submit an application\Nwith a clean conscience,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.57,0:05:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,confident that Jehovah\Nwill bless your efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.86,0:05:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So don’t hesitate to speak
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.97,0:05:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,with one of the elders\Nin your congregation if you need help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.37,0:05:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They love you\Nand want you to progress and qualify
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.75,0:05:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,for special privileges\Nof service in Jehovah’s organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.71,0:05:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We’ve spoken frankly to you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.78,0:05:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,because we want you\Nto make a success
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.15,0:05:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,of your service to Jehovah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.43,0:05:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We also want to reassure you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.85,0:05:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,that your assistance\Nis very much needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.22,0:05:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you enjoy good health,\Nboth spiritually and physically,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.10,0:05:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and want to apply\Nfor expanded theocratic service
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.90,0:06:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,on a temporary or full-time basis,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.90,0:06:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,ask your elders for an application
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.91,0:06:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,to serve as a temporary volunteer
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.33,0:06:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,or as a member of the Worldwide Order
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.25,0:06:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,of Special Full-Time Servants
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,of Jehovah’s Witnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.75,0:06:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,After completing the application,\Nreturn it to your elders.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.09,0:06:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Then continue to allow Jehovah
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.24,0:06:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,to direct your steps\Nwherever you may serve.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.82,0:06:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We love you\Nfor the willing spirit you show.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.35,0:06:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be assured\Nof our prayers in your behalf
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.98,0:06:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,as you continue\Nto reach out in Jehovah’s service.
